snippet.title: maybe : Interactive Stories | Keeper of Mine Ep 1
snippet.description:
From an average white-collar to a villainess in a novel. You jump into the world of a fantasy romance novel to help your favorite character achieve love. But the storyline becomes entangled and it's time for you to create a happy ending!
